@startuml AlternativeSequence_Detailed
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Детальная Sequence Diagram: Получение рекомендаций

actor "Покупатель" as Customer
participant "Web App" as WebApp
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "AI Service\nAPI Controller" as Controller
participant "Auth\nMiddleware" as Auth
participant "Recommendation\nEngine" as Engine
participant "Cache\nManager" as Cache
participant "Vector DB\nClient" as VectorClient
participant "RAG\nManager" as RAG
participant "LLM\nClient" as LLM
database "Redis" as Redis
database "Qdrant" as Qdrant
database "MySQL" as MySQL

Customer -> WebApp: Открывает главную страницу
activate WebApp

WebApp -> Gateway: GET /api/recommendations\n?user_id=123&context=homepage&limit=10
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Controller: Маршрутизирует запрос
activate Controller

Controller -> Auth: Проверить JWT токен
activate Auth
Auth --> Controller: Токен валиден
deactivate Auth

Controller -> Engine: getRecommendations(userId=123,\ncontext="homepage", limit=10)
activate Engine

Engine -> Cache: checkCache("user:123:homepage")
activate Cache
Cache -> Redis: GET user:123:homepage
activate Redis
Redis --> Cache: null (cache miss)
deactivate Redis
Cache --> Engine: Кэш не найден
deactivate Cache

Engine -> VectorClient: findSimilarProducts(userId=123, k=20)
activate VectorClient
VectorClient -> Qdrant: search(user_embedding, top_k=20)
activate Qdrant
Qdrant --> VectorClient: [product_ids + scores]
deactivate Qdrant
VectorClient --> Engine: Список похожих товаров
deactivate VectorClient

Engine -> MySQL: SELECT * FROM products\nWHERE id IN (...)
activate MySQL
MySQL --> Engine: Метаданные товаров\n(цены, наличие, категории)
deactivate MySQL

Engine -> RAG: generatePersonalizedContent(\nuser=123, products=[...])
activate RAG

RAG -> LLM: generate(prompt=\n"Создай персонализированное описание...")
activate LLM
LLM --> RAG: "Иван, на основе ваших\nинтересов к ноутбукам..."
deactivate LLM

RAG --> Engine: Персонализированный текст
deactivate RAG

Engine -> Engine: Формирует итоговый\nответ с top-10

Engine -> Cache: saveToCache("user:123:homepage",\nresult, TTL=300s)
activate Cache
Cache -> Redis: SETEX user:123:homepage 300 {...}
activate Redis
Redis --> Cache: OK
deactivate Redis
deactivate Cache

Engine --> Controller: RecommendationResponse
deactivate Engine

Controller --> Gateway: HTTP 200 OK\n{recommendations: [...]}
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> WebApp: JSON Response
deactivate Gateway

WebApp --> Customer: Отображает блок\n"Специально для вас"
deactivate WebApp

@enduml